There is a orange cat that has attached itself to our house.

He now has attached himself to me...

He seems to despise my Grandma....

He likes it when I pet him and seems to have an obsession with the curves of my body. He constantly rubs his face against my chest, rear, and thighs. If I try to leave him, I have to beg him because if I don't beg he doesn't let me go and bites me.

If I open the front door he is waiting for me outside.

When he sees me he runs towards me and jumps up like a poodle trying to attack my hand with his skull.

Funny...Cats don't usually like me...Must be the turkey and milk...

I named him Kyounkichi.

So I was sitting on Nick's lap and Nina said I was a belly warmer. Nick said I was his extra warmth xD After being in the hot tub, Nick gave me a piggy back ride as we jumped into the Icecube Water, Kristina whom had already been in there was cracking up. Then Nick yelled and climbed out of the water with me still on his back but Nina grabbed my shirt and pulled us back in. We ran out and I slipped on some water and fucked up my leg, of course...Me being the noble person I am I simply put on my BRAVE FACE and beared the pain! Lmfao LAST! LMFAO Then Nina left to go talk with her MAMA and Nick said something about the FATMAN and I cracked up resulting with my face in his chest laughing.
